1
00:00:03,950 --> 00:00:06,899
♫ <i> Nowhere to escape </i> ♫

2
00:00:06,899 --> 00:00:09,859
♫ <i> No one to rely on </i> ♫

3
00:00:09,859 --> 00:00:14,930
♫ <i> Withdrawing smiles </i> ♫

4
00:00:15,860 --> 00:00:18,770
♫ <i> Never give in </i> ♫

5
00:00:18,770 --> 00:00:24,950
♫ <i> Forget about one's youth </i> ♫

6
00:00:25,850 --> 00:00:28,820
♫ <i> I've never been afraid of loneliness when
embarking on this journey </i> ♫

7
00:00:28,820 --> 00:00:31,689
♫ <i> Tears and regrets go hand in hand </i> ♫

8
00:00:31,689 --> 00:00:34,690
♫ <i>But my heart is still fiery-hot</i> ♫

9
00:00:34,690 --> 00:00:37,740
♫ <i>To the distance</i> ♫

10
00:00:37,740 --> 00:00:40,709
♫ <i>The miserable past is like a dagger</i> ♫

11
00:00:40,709 --> 00:00:43,619
♫ <i>Though my wings are broken</i> ♫

12
00:00:43,619 --> 00:00:51,040
♫ <i>I will keep flying</i> ♫

13
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:56,099
♫ <i>Following the direction of the light</i> ♫

14
00:00:56,099 --> 00:00:58,359
♫ <i>I'll forget you</i> ♫

15
00:00:58,360 --> 00:01:04,360
♫ <i>The memory shaped my stubbornness</i> ♫

16
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:07,359
♫ <i>By virtue of the light in the dark night</i> ♫

17
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:10,309
♫ <i>I'll return it with a long ballad</i> ♫

18
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:12,370
♫ <i>The river of life is under my feet</i> ♫

19
00:01:12,370 --> 00:01:17,960
♫ <i>I don't regret my craziness</i> ♫

20
00:01:26,230 --> 00:01:32,699
<i>[The Long Ballad]</i>

21
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:36,259
<i>[Episode 27]</i>

22
00:01:36,260 --> 00:01:39,340
<i>[Luoyang Office]</i>

23
00:01:55,059 --> 00:01:57,019
Xiao Wu.

24
00:02:00,379 --> 00:02:02,419
Wait for me.

25
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:12,039
Xiao Wu. Xiao Wu.

26
00:02:15,019 --> 00:02:17,260
Wait for me.

27
00:02:17,260 --> 00:02:18,799
Don't leave me.

28
00:02:18,799 --> 00:02:21,020
Xiao Wu.

29
00:02:23,340 --> 00:02:25,280
Xiao Wu.

30
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:30,759
Princess. Princess.

31
00:02:33,479 --> 00:02:35,560
Forgive me, please.

32
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:39,319
Where is Xiao Wu? Where is Xiao Wu?

33
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:41,298
I've ordered them to bury Xiao Wu.

34
00:02:41,298 --> 00:02:43,239
Please rest at ease.

35
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:01,840
I just had a dream.

36
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:05,120
In the dream, Xiao Wu was still alive.

37
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:08,498
But I don't know why he's running.

38
00:03:08,498 --> 00:03:13,440
He keeps running and doesn't want to come back to me.

39
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:22,479
Hao Du, is he still blaming me?

40
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:24,780
If not for me,

41
00:03:24,780 --> 00:03:29,440
he wouldn't have been wounded and sick for long.

42
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:35,340
He would have lived well.

43
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:46,799
I promised to give him a cart of rice.

44
00:03:46,799 --> 00:03:49,259
I would take him to Chang'an

45
00:03:49,259 --> 00:03:53,620
to see the blooming spring and picturesque landscape.

46
00:03:53,620 --> 00:04:00,399
Now... it's all gone.

47
00:04:01,119 --> 00:04:05,019
Princess, he left with a smile.

48
00:04:05,019 --> 00:04:06,720
He didn't blame you.

49
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:09,119
Don't be sad.

50
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:14,920
Take me to him tomorrow.

51
00:04:16,559 --> 00:04:19,319
I want to be by his side until the end.

52
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:23,979
Princess, you're not scared of me now?

53
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:31,240
After all these things, I'm not scared of death.

54
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:34,660
You? I'm not scared.

55
00:04:36,119 --> 00:04:39,719
I was scared of many things in the past.

56
00:04:39,719 --> 00:04:45,040
Thinking of it, how ridiculous I was.

57
00:04:48,559 --> 00:04:51,740
Heaven rewards the good.

58
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:56,139
I've been guided to you by this amulet.

59
00:04:56,139 --> 00:04:57,458
Now I return it to you.

60
00:04:57,459 --> 00:05:00,279
I wish it a blessing to you.

61
00:05:04,619 --> 00:05:06,458
Why do you have it?

62
00:05:06,459 --> 00:05:08,239
It's a long story.

63
00:05:08,239 --> 00:05:10,379
I found it in Hongyi Palace.

64
00:05:10,379 --> 00:05:14,179
Maybe it's God's will.

65
00:05:14,179 --> 00:05:17,740
If God pities me,

66
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:22,920
please bless the peace of all people.

67
00:05:23,939 --> 00:05:25,220
I'm sure he will.

68
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:26,760
God will bless Great Tang.

69
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,939
It's God's will.

70
00:05:30,679 --> 00:05:32,800
Take it.

71
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:38,579
I hope it works till the end.

72
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,379
Please don't be upset.

73
00:05:41,379 --> 00:05:42,618
Take care of yourself.

74
00:05:42,619 --> 00:05:46,258
I've been ordered to find a servant you're most familiar with to take care of you.

75
00:05:46,258 --> 00:05:48,400
She'll be here soon.

76
00:05:50,020 --> 00:05:51,920
Thanks a lot.

77
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:03,919
Honestly, it's very lucky for you to come here.

78
00:06:03,919 --> 00:06:04,859
You know what?

79
00:06:04,860 --> 00:06:07,778
Liuyun Taoist Temple is a blessed land in the world.

80
00:06:07,779 --> 00:06:09,859
It's perfect with kindness and insight,

81
00:06:09,860 --> 00:06:12,820
delivers all living creatures from difficulty.

82
00:06:12,820 --> 00:06:15,740
You aren't listening to me, are you?

83
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,840
How rude this apprentice is.

84
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:24,220
<i>[Yuqing's Utmost Taoist]</i>

85
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:33,720
<i>[Great virtues match Heaven and Earth.]</i>

86
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,398
Nice to meet you, Taoist Sun.

87
00:06:36,398 --> 00:06:39,458
Master has been talking about you. Finally, you're here.

88
00:06:39,458 --> 00:06:41,658
Go to tell Master Taoist Sun's coming.

89
00:06:41,659 --> 00:06:43,459
Okay.

90
00:06:43,459 --> 00:06:46,180
Let's go inside.

91
00:06:46,180 --> 00:06:48,960
This lady is...

92
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:52,260
She was picked by me.

93
00:06:55,259 --> 00:06:59,340
She's in a bad mood; touchy now.

94
00:07:03,739 --> 00:07:06,420
Please come in.

95
00:07:12,799 --> 00:07:15,080
Are you better now?

96
00:07:17,899 --> 00:07:20,700
Eat something.

97
00:07:20,700 --> 00:07:23,140
Eat it.

98
00:07:23,140 --> 00:07:24,959
Slow down.

99
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:31,719
Here, we help refugees.

100
00:07:31,719 --> 00:07:33,959
They're very pitiful.

101
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:36,659
We help the poor people.

102
00:07:37,359 --> 00:07:39,059
This way.

103
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,539
Liuyun Taoist Temple is divided into three yards.

104
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:54,600
Front, middle, and back.

105
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:58,139
This is the pharmacy, opposite Taoist Sun's exam room,

106
00:07:58,139 --> 00:08:00,200
which is connected to the exam rooms in the front yard.

107
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:03,220
This is where Master lives.

108
00:08:03,220 --> 00:08:05,920
Let's go to the backyard.

109
00:08:13,739 --> 00:08:16,420
This is the backyard.

110
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:21,419
It's silent here with many rooms.

111
00:08:21,419 --> 00:08:25,220
You can choose one to live in.

112
00:08:25,220 --> 00:08:30,159
If you find yourself bored, come to me and A'Bi.

113
00:08:37,940 --> 00:08:39,980
<i>[Non-interference]</i>

114
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:58,700
What are you looking at?

115
00:08:58,700 --> 00:09:00,819
What is this place?

116
00:09:00,819 --> 00:09:02,898
Master always meditates here.

117
00:09:02,899 --> 00:09:05,380
We call it the Silence Room.

118
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:12,600
<i>[Non-interference]</i>

119
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:15,260
Then let me live here.

120
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:35,190
<i>[Dear Brother Xiao Wu]</i>

121
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,660
Princess.

122
00:10:07,259 --> 00:10:09,320
Death is final.

123
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,480
My condolences.

124
00:10:12,679 --> 00:10:16,038
Please don't blame yourself.

125
00:10:16,038 --> 00:10:17,939
He had an unkind fate.

126
00:10:17,939 --> 00:10:20,119
He took care of you a lot.

127
00:10:20,119 --> 00:10:22,459
He was a righteous man.

128
00:10:24,219 --> 00:10:26,338
If you can't reconcile with yourself,

129
00:10:26,339 --> 00:10:30,080
we can ask for a reward for him when we arrive in Chang'an.

130
00:10:31,860 --> 00:10:34,199
He won't care about that.

131
00:10:34,199 --> 00:10:36,260
Besides...

132
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:39,320
he's gone.

133
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:41,679
It's useless.

134
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:47,839
I hope one day that everyone in Great Tang won't need to

135
00:10:47,839 --> 00:10:51,919
suffer from war, coldness, hunger, homelessness, or misery.

136
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:57,919
I hope everyone has food to eat, fields to farm

137
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:03,999
with no theft or danger.

138
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:07,499
I think it will be happy and peaceful days.

139
00:11:07,499 --> 00:11:09,140
It will be.

140
00:11:09,140 --> 00:11:11,459
We'll have that day.

141
00:11:28,659 --> 00:11:33,259
Xiao Wu, I'll eat this bowl of rice for you.

142
00:11:34,719 --> 00:11:40,339
You won't be hungry anymore with so much rice.

143
00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:06,220
<i>[Dear Brother Xiao Wu]</i>

144
00:12:18,350 --> 00:12:21,520
<i>I'm not a disloyal man.</i>

145
00:12:23,370 --> 00:12:25,000
<i>I didn't recognize you.</i>

146
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,970
<i>I apologize to you for my sister.</i>

147
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:33,400
<i>With me, you can't be starving, can you?</i>

148
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:47,219
<i>[Dear Brother Xiao Wu]</i>

149
00:12:47,220 --> 00:12:50,920
<i>[Luoyang Office]</i>

150
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:21,769
Finally you're here, Princess.

151
00:13:21,769 --> 00:13:23,689
I was so worried about you.

152
00:13:23,690 --> 00:13:25,329
Thank God.

153
00:13:25,330 --> 00:13:27,280
Please take a bath and put on clean clothes.

154
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:29,790
I'll help you.

155
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:34,009
Why are you crying?

156
00:13:34,010 --> 00:13:36,800
I'm okay now.

157
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:39,939
I'm so glad to see you, Princess.

158
00:13:39,940 --> 00:13:42,919
Take a rest first. I can do it myself.

159
00:13:42,919 --> 00:13:44,380
But...

160
00:13:44,380 --> 00:13:46,280
I can do it.

161
00:13:46,280 --> 00:13:51,049
Okay. Call me anytime if you need me.

162
00:14:03,350 --> 00:14:05,859
Princess rests here tonight.

163
00:14:05,859 --> 00:14:07,979
Keep your eyes open.

164
00:14:07,980 --> 00:14:09,480
Yes, sir!

165
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:22,840
Who's the commander?

166
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:29,379
What brings you here so late at night?

167
00:14:29,380 --> 00:14:30,649
A royal warrant.

168
00:14:30,650 --> 00:14:32,340
I dare not waste time.

169
00:14:32,340 --> 00:14:34,640
Please receive it, Commander.

170
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:42,560
<i>[I've seen your report. I ordered the crown prince to Luoyang to inspect around counties for the damage for me.]</i>

171
00:14:49,740 --> 00:14:53,159
Thanks a lot. Please report for me.

172
00:14:53,159 --> 00:14:56,379
Princess Yongan has been found in Luoyang. She's fine.

173
00:14:56,379 --> 00:14:58,650
Please rest assured.

174
00:14:58,650 --> 00:15:00,270
Yes.

175
00:15:59,890 --> 00:16:03,560
Forgive me, please. I forgot you were...

176
00:16:04,910 --> 00:16:08,249
I'll send some guards for you tomorrow. To protect you.

177
00:16:08,249 --> 00:16:10,740
I came here for...

178
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:15,400
- I'll come tomorrow.
- Wait.

179
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:18,299
It's late now. You must have come here because of an emergency.

180
00:16:18,299 --> 00:16:19,830
Yes.

181
00:16:20,900 --> 00:16:23,670
I just received a handwritten letter from His Majesty from Chang'an.

182
00:16:23,670 --> 00:16:25,770
Please have a look.

183
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:32,139
Crown Prince has left Chang'an to inspect the damage to show grace on behalf of His Majesty.

184
00:16:32,139 --> 00:16:34,640
He'll arrive in a few days.

185
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:37,149
Thank you for delivering the letter, Young Master Hao.

186
00:16:37,149 --> 00:16:39,540
I'll read it later.

187
00:16:39,540 --> 00:16:44,240
In that case, I won't hurry to go back.

188
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:46,750
The crown prince is young and naughty.

189
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:48,880
I have to look after him.

190
00:16:48,880 --> 00:16:50,670
I can help you with that.

191
00:16:50,670 --> 00:16:54,150
- But...
- I've decided it.

192
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:57,890
You have to stay with me in Luoyang for a while, Young Master Hao.

193
00:16:58,710 --> 00:17:02,200
Princess, you've changed a lot.

194
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:06,380
What happened is a mixed blessing.

195
00:17:06,380 --> 00:17:09,010
I lost, I gained.

196
00:17:09,010 --> 00:17:12,470
Now I know what Father often said to me.

197
00:17:12,470 --> 00:17:16,550
People live hard. How can we stand by?

198
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:19,200
I'm his daughter.

199
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:22,160
How can I stay ignorant?

200
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:25,530
You've suffered a great deal, haven't you?

201
00:17:25,530 --> 00:17:28,680
I met many difficulties

202
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:32,050
and many people to express my gratitude, as well.

203
00:17:32,050 --> 00:17:34,350
Difficulties will be gone,

204
00:17:34,350 --> 00:17:40,500
but the gratitude will be cherished in my heart forever.

205
00:17:42,100 --> 00:17:46,250
In the past, I only saw people's appearance.

206
00:17:46,250 --> 00:17:51,140
Now I know I need to see what's in their mind.

207
00:17:51,140 --> 00:17:55,460
Someone seems kind but hides a malicious heart.

208
00:17:55,460 --> 00:18:00,170
Someone has a cold face but a kind heart.

209
00:18:01,430 --> 00:18:04,000
Just like you, Young Master Hao.

210
00:18:11,670 --> 00:18:14,390
<i>[Silence Room]</i>

211
00:19:12,619 --> 00:19:14,979
Why can't I master it?

212
00:19:14,979 --> 00:19:16,439
<i>Your Dao is different.
(T/N: Dao: Taoism teaches about the various disciplines for achieving "perfection" by becoming one with the unplanned rhythms of the universe)</i>

213
00:19:16,439 --> 00:19:19,319
<i>You can't do it. Give up now.</i>

214
00:19:19,319 --> 00:19:21,580
Different Dao?

215
00:19:21,580 --> 00:19:24,120
Where's the difference?

216
00:19:25,520 --> 00:19:30,420
<i>In your opinion, what's my reason to defend Shuozhou?</i>

217
00:19:30,420 --> 00:19:35,380
<i>Fights or surrenders are just the means</i>

218
00:19:35,380 --> 00:19:38,079
<i>to guarantee that the citizens stay away from war and live a happy life.</i>

219
00:19:38,079 --> 00:19:40,200
<i>These are the most important.</i>

220
00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:45,460
<i>This is the Dao I stick to.</i>

221
00:19:52,150 --> 00:19:58,520
<i>[Non-interference]</i>

222
00:19:59,719 --> 00:20:02,319
What exactly is my Dao?

223
00:20:07,059 --> 00:20:09,998
Senior Qin, did Yuan fall asleep?

224
00:20:09,998 --> 00:20:12,559
- Yes.
- Okay.

225
00:20:12,559 --> 00:20:15,099
We asked Luo Shiba to share messages with us.

226
00:20:15,100 --> 00:20:18,338
But when we sent the message, she never wrote back.

227
00:20:18,339 --> 00:20:22,079
Now she suddenly wanted to see us and would bring a friend to us.

228
00:20:22,079 --> 00:20:24,130
A friend?

229
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:27,178
We have no progress so far.

230
00:20:27,179 --> 00:20:33,239
Maybe this friend can bring some messages of Young Master.

231
00:20:40,359 --> 00:20:43,000
Luo Shiba, here you are.

232
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:45,439
Your friend is...

233
00:20:48,760 --> 00:20:49,959
Luo Shiba.

234
00:20:49,959 --> 00:20:53,320
This is your friend?

235
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:57,940
Everyone listen, kill Ashile Sun to take revenge for the governor.

236
00:20:58,599 --> 00:21:00,499
Wait.

237
00:21:07,740 --> 00:21:10,940
About Gongsun Heng, I have a clear conscience.

238
00:21:10,940 --> 00:21:12,779
Now Changge is missing.

239
00:21:12,780 --> 00:21:15,739
I come here only to find her.

240
00:21:15,740 --> 00:21:17,380
Find her?

241
00:21:17,380 --> 00:21:19,218
It's you who took her to the grassland

242
00:21:19,219 --> 00:21:22,039
where she encountered misery, isn't it?

243
00:21:22,039 --> 00:21:25,798
Luo Shiba, you don't know what Ashile Tribe means to us, do you?

244
00:21:25,798 --> 00:21:27,439
How can you bring him to Great Tang?

245
00:21:27,439 --> 00:21:29,180
I only want to find her.

246
00:21:29,180 --> 00:21:32,379
I'll find a way to find her even without your help.

247
00:21:32,380 --> 00:21:34,080
You...

248
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:36,998
Ashile Sun, answer me.

249
00:21:36,998 --> 00:21:41,238
Did you provoke by posting up the notice that Commandant Li sacrificed for the country?

250
00:21:41,238 --> 00:21:43,159
It was me.

251
00:21:44,900 --> 00:21:47,999
It was the best way to defend Commandant Li.

252
00:21:47,999 --> 00:21:51,659
So what's your purpose to find her?

253
00:21:51,659 --> 00:21:53,879
I have no purpose.

254
00:21:53,879 --> 00:21:59,160
Only because... she's my friend.

255
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:01,320
Friend?

256
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:04,480
Commandant Li is your friend?

257
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:06,938
Senior Qin, you're confused by him.

258
00:22:06,938 --> 00:22:09,319
Do you believe he's a friend of Commandant Li's?

259
00:22:09,319 --> 00:22:14,279
You should know how the whole city reviled Commandant Li.

260
00:22:14,279 --> 00:22:19,839
It's Ashile Tribe's notice that subsided their rage.

