365
00:27:07,639 --> 00:27:09,040
Yes.

366
00:27:13,140 --> 00:27:15,560
<i>They are killing us!</i>

367
00:27:15,560 --> 00:27:19,958
<i>Guards are killing us. People are dying.</i>

368
00:27:19,958 --> 00:27:21,899
Young Master Wei, what should we do?

369
00:27:21,900 --> 00:27:23,698
His Highness left us behind.

370
00:27:23,699 --> 00:27:25,178
We'll die of hunger in Luoyang.

371
00:27:25,179 --> 00:27:26,578
Nobody cares about us.

372
00:27:26,579 --> 00:27:28,219
