374
00:27:30,460 --> 00:27:33,820
His Highness will never leave you behind.

375
00:27:34,579 --> 00:27:36,359
<i>Is it true?</i>

376
00:27:38,020 --> 00:27:38,839
<i>Really?</i>

377
00:27:38,839 --> 00:27:40,040
You're talking nonsense.

378
00:27:40,040 --> 00:27:42,840
His Highness does not care about us.

379
00:27:42,840 --> 00:27:45,859
<i>He's right. He doesn't care.</i>

380
00:27:45,859 --> 00:27:48,858
<i>We want food! He doesn't care!</i>

381
00:27:49,860 --> 00:27:51,760
<i>We want food!</i>

382
00:27:53,020 --> 00:27:54,800
<i>Give food to us.</i>

383
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:13,499
<i>[Luoyang Office]</i>

384
00:28:13,499 --> 00:28:16,320
The noble who can save you is coming.

385
00:28:22,300 --> 00:28:25,058
Tell us what you want.

386
00:28:25,059 --> 00:28:28,040
Why do you make a disturbance outside the office?

387
00:28:28,040 --> 00:28:29,659
Who are you?

388
00:28:29,660 --> 00:28:31,578
His Highness doesn't care about us.

389
00:28:31,579 --> 00:28:33,499
How can you keep your word?

390
00:28:33,500 --> 00:28:34,178
<i>Yes. He's right.</i>

391
00:28:34,179 --> 00:28:35,420
<i>His Highness doesn't care about us.</i>

392
00:28:35,420 --> 00:28:38,059
<i>- What can you do? Am I right? Yes.
- Yes.</i>

393
00:28:38,059 --> 00:28:39,259
- Please listen to me.
<i>- What can you do?</i>

394
00:28:39,260 --> 00:28:40,259
<i>What can you do?</i>

395
00:28:40,259 --> 00:28:42,640
I'm Princess Yongan of Great Tang.

396
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:44,420
You have my word.

397
00:28:44,420 --> 00:28:47,079
This country will never leave you alone.

398
00:28:47,079 --> 00:28:48,818
Please don't worry.

399
00:28:48,819 --> 00:28:52,779
Food, water, clothes, and beds. You'll have them all.

400
00:28:52,780 --> 00:28:56,680
We have to face the difficulties of Luoyang together.

401
00:28:58,339 --> 00:29:00,299
<i>Really?</i>

402
00:29:01,579 --> 00:29:02,938
<i>We won't die of hunger.</i>

403
00:29:02,939 --> 00:29:04,739
<i>Yes.</i>

404
00:29:14,219 --> 00:29:16,239
What are you doing?

405
00:29:16,239 --> 00:29:19,879
Your wound will fester if the bleeding doesn't stop.

406
00:29:21,539 --> 00:29:23,518
- Don't move.
- I don't need it!

407
00:29:25,179 --> 00:29:26,679
Hao Du.

408
00:29:33,900 --> 00:29:36,979
You pretend to be injured and agitate these people.

409
00:29:36,980 --> 00:29:38,820
What's your purpose?

410
00:29:39,499 --> 00:29:40,999
Answer me.

411
00:29:43,460 --> 00:29:46,420
Very good. You don't answer me.

412
00:29:46,420 --> 00:29:48,540
Then never answer me.

413
00:29:48,540 --> 00:29:52,300
Hao Du, he did that because of starvation and fear.

414
00:29:52,300 --> 00:29:54,119
Don't hurt him.

415
00:29:59,580 --> 00:30:01,060
Do you see that?

416
00:30:01,060 --> 00:30:03,160
Her Highness sympathizes with these kinds of people.

417
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:05,520
How can Her Highness leave you alone?

418
00:30:06,819 --> 00:30:08,920
<i>Yes. He's right. Yes.</i>

419
00:30:22,580 --> 00:30:24,719
<i>Brother Shuyu.</i>

420
00:30:38,039 --> 00:30:40,680
Yueyan, it's you.

421
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:43,480
It's great. You're finally here.

422
00:30:49,900 --> 00:30:52,119
I've been looking for you for such a long time.

423
00:30:52,119 --> 00:30:54,178
I almost missed no relevant inch in the north lands.

424
00:30:54,179 --> 00:30:56,219
I was afraid of losing you.

425
00:30:57,499 --> 00:31:01,640
Sorry, it's all my fault.

426
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:06,060
I lost you and made you suffer a lot.

427
00:31:06,060 --> 00:31:08,900
Brother Shuyu, it's not your fault.

428
00:31:08,900 --> 00:31:12,299
No one predicts good or bad fortune.

429
00:31:12,299 --> 00:31:15,540
See? I'm fine.

