440
00:31:57,760 --> 00:32:00,960
Princess, please go and see the crown prince.

441
00:32:23,499 --> 00:32:24,660
Your Highness.

442
00:32:24,660 --> 00:32:27,298
His Highness asked me to tell Your Highness that

443
00:32:27,299 --> 00:32:30,379
His Highness is scared and suddenly has a fever.

444
00:32:30,380 --> 00:32:32,218
