447
00:32:35,780 --> 00:32:37,380
Yes.

448
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:40,119
Your Highness.

449
00:32:40,119 --> 00:32:43,420
His Highness was afraid of passing it to Your Highness.

450
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:45,959
Her Highness visits her younger brother. How dare you block the way?

451
00:32:45,959 --> 00:32:48,139
If His Highness's condition is delayed,

452
00:32:48,140 --> 00:32:50,539
