453
00:33:23,660 --> 00:33:25,420
Don't pretend in front of me.

454
00:33:30,579 --> 00:33:32,200
Sister.

455
00:33:34,219 --> 00:33:36,439
Father sent you to Luoyang

456
00:33:36,439 --> 00:33:39,060
to console the people who are suffering from the drought,

457
00:33:39,060 --> 00:33:41,418
and build your image as a crown prince.

458
00:33:41,419 --> 00:33:42,779
You're pretending to be ill here.

459
00:33:42,780 --> 00:33:44,719
How could you do that?

460
00:33:46,419 --> 00:33:48,580
Sister, you've seen that.

461
00:33:48,580 --> 00:33:51,920
These people are not poor men but gangsters.

462
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:54,120
Look at them. With blood all over their faces,

463
00:33:54,120 --> 00:33:55,659
they're making threatening gestures.

464
00:33:55,660 --> 00:33:56,859
They've scared me to death.

465
00:33:56,860 --> 00:34:00,139
Just thinking of them, my head is aching.

466
00:34:01,459 --> 00:34:03,260
I'm not going anywhere.

467
00:34:05,099 --> 00:34:09,899
Brother, I know that as a child,

468
00:34:09,899 --> 00:34:13,239
when you're facing such situations, you'll be scared.

469
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:16,498
But you need to know that sooner or later,

470
00:34:16,499 --> 00:34:19,120
we have to take on the responsibilities on our own,

471
00:34:19,120 --> 00:34:21,239
especially for you.

472
00:34:24,339 --> 00:34:26,338
I know, Sister.

473
00:34:26,339 --> 00:34:27,559
