486
00:35:00,059 --> 00:35:04,880
Brother, do you know what a crown prince is?

487
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:09,540
It means you're the future of the country.

488
00:35:09,540 --> 00:35:13,559
And you'll be the leader of our people.

489
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:18,239
Be a man, brother, like our father.

490
00:35:18,239 --> 00:35:19,920
Win the trust of our people.

491
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:22,460
And be a wise emperor.

492
00:35:40,860 --> 00:35:42,260
Hao Du.

493
00:35:47,140 --> 00:35:49,398
You found Yueyan first.

494
00:35:49,398 --> 00:35:50,899
Thank you.

495
00:35:52,299 --> 00:35:55,700
