522
00:37:24,499 --> 00:37:26,239
I'll check her out.

523
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:30,619
Good to see you, Mr. Situ.

524
00:37:31,099 --> 00:37:32,799
Master.

525
00:37:32,799 --> 00:37:35,859
Can I talk to her?

526
00:37:41,120 --> 00:37:46,860
<i>[Non-interference]</i>

527
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:01,820
The night you came,

528
00:38:01,820 --> 00:38:04,400
I was just passing by.

529
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:08,139
I saw you practicing swordsmanship in the middle of the night.

530
00:38:08,139 --> 00:38:14,580
You've stayed in the Silence Room ever since you came to our temple.

531
00:38:15,320 --> 00:38:17,479
Do you have any thoughts?

532
00:38:18,140 --> 00:38:21,220
I've been taught by my teacher since childhood.

533
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:23,799
I've read books from all classes of authors.

534
00:38:24,660 --> 00:38:27,720
I've never liked the thought of non-interference of Taoism.

535
00:38:27,720 --> 00:38:31,520
To struggle with people, you can find your refuge.

536
00:38:31,520 --> 00:38:35,619
To struggle with people, you can achieve your pursuit.

537
00:38:36,539 --> 00:38:38,560
For all these years,

538
00:38:38,560 --> 00:38:40,999
I've held a strong belief in it.

539
00:38:41,900 --> 00:38:44,380
But in these few days,

540
00:38:44,380 --> 00:38:46,400
I started to realize that

541
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:49,420
I was wrong.

542
00:38:51,919 --> 00:38:54,219
If I hadn't struggled,

543
00:38:54,219 --> 00:38:59,800
someone like my real brother wouldn't have died for me.

544
00:39:02,199 --> 00:39:04,220
If I hadn't struggled,

545
00:39:04,220 --> 00:39:09,079
someone who has treated me like his daughter wouldn't have died for me.

546
00:39:09,719 --> 00:39:11,700
If I hadn't struggled,

547
00:39:11,700 --> 00:39:16,850
someone who had given all he had to me wouldn't have been in danger,

548
00:39:19,479 --> 00:39:24,500
while his dear family wouldn't have died for me as well.

549
00:39:25,840 --> 00:39:30,720
One senior saved my life

550
00:39:31,760 --> 00:39:34,679
and taught me to find my own Tao.

551
00:39:34,679 --> 00:39:36,679
Non-interference.

552
00:39:37,520 --> 00:39:39,579
This is the way.

553
00:39:41,439 --> 00:39:43,540
God bless us all.

554
00:39:43,540 --> 00:39:48,679
If you really think in this way, you've spent some good time

555
00:39:48,679 --> 00:39:51,678
in this Silence Room.

556
00:39:51,678 --> 00:39:53,959
What about now?

557
00:39:55,479 --> 00:39:58,679
Dead people are gone forever.

558
00:39:58,679 --> 00:40:01,360
I've wasted so much time on this.

559
00:40:01,360 --> 00:40:05,219
It's really precious for us to be enlightened.

560
00:40:05,220 --> 00:40:08,699
There are lots of refugees in Luoyang.

561
00:40:08,700 --> 00:40:11,659
We're busy helping those in need.

562
00:40:11,659 --> 00:40:14,439
If you have time,

563
00:40:14,439 --> 00:40:18,039
you can help me and Taoist Sun.

564
00:40:18,039 --> 00:40:21,519
Everything in Taoism is about people.

565
00:40:21,519 --> 00:40:24,120
We should appreciate the world we live in.

566
00:40:24,120 --> 00:40:29,100
Dwelling in the past will only bring you more trouble.

567
00:40:39,940 --> 00:40:43,220
<i>[Non-interference]</i>

568
00:41:05,779 --> 00:41:07,679
From the way she talks,

569
00:41:07,679 --> 00:41:10,298
Master must know that she is not an ordinary person.

570
00:41:10,299 --> 00:41:14,519
Do you want to hear more about her story?

571
00:41:14,519 --> 00:41:17,138
What are you talking about?

572
00:41:17,138 --> 00:41:18,419
Things come and go.

573
00:41:18,419 --> 00:41:20,600
People come and go, too.

574
00:41:20,600 --> 00:41:22,780
I've never asked.

575
00:41:22,780 --> 00:41:24,578
But I do miss the old times.

576
00:41:24,579 --> 00:41:27,440
When I was of her age,

577
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:32,799
I also regarded myself as the smartest person in the world.

578
00:41:34,259 --> 00:41:39,420
It seems that you and she have some connections.

579
00:41:39,420 --> 00:41:42,119
Tell me about it.

580
00:41:42,119 --> 00:41:44,718
In this world, we all come and go.

581
00:41:44,718 --> 00:41:47,099
We share the same fate.

582
00:41:47,639 --> 00:41:51,478
Will you come to South Hill with me tomorrow?

583
00:41:51,478 --> 00:41:55,800
I heard that there are more refugees than we have here.

584
00:41:56,660 --> 00:41:57,659
Sure.

585
00:41:57,660 --> 00:42:03,440
If we can encounter some rare diseases, that'll be worth trying.

586
00:42:04,259 --> 00:42:05,959
Have some tea.

587
00:42:10,420 --> 00:42:12,859
I'm so glad to see you eat something.

588
00:42:12,860 --> 00:42:14,338
I've been worried about you.

589
00:42:14,339 --> 00:42:18,978
I heard that Taoist Sun has tried so hard to save you.

590
00:42:18,979 --> 00:42:21,139
Would you like to get changed now?

591
00:42:43,059 --> 00:42:44,659
Isn't it beautiful?

592
00:42:44,660 --> 00:42:47,519
Liuyun Taoist Temple is the most beautiful place in Luoyang.

593
00:42:47,519 --> 00:42:51,438
The one you just talked to is our master, Taoist Jingdan.

594
00:42:51,438 --> 00:42:54,699
She has sheltered many refugees suffering from the drought.

595
00:42:54,700 --> 00:42:56,640
She is such a nice person.

596
00:42:57,420 --> 00:42:59,538
She wants to know your plan for the future.

597
00:42:59,539 --> 00:43:02,799
Taoist Sun is going to stay in Luoyang for some days.

598
00:43:02,799 --> 00:43:06,540
Are you going back to your hometown or staying here?

599
00:43:07,120 --> 00:43:12,139
My hometown is somewhere I can never go back.

600
00:43:14,040 --> 00:43:15,260
I'll stay.

601
00:43:15,260 --> 00:43:17,779
That'll be great. I've got a mate.

602
00:43:17,779 --> 00:43:21,538
Except for us, Tianjing and Liu'er also live here.

603
00:43:21,539 --> 00:43:23,160
We're about the same age.

604
00:43:23,160 --> 00:43:25,659
We can be good friends.

605
00:43:25,659 --> 00:43:28,499
I'm A'Bi from Family Wang. What's your name?

606
00:43:29,560 --> 00:43:32,299
<i>Since Changge is no longer in Great Tang,</i>

607
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:36,000
<i>I'd avoid some troubles.</i>

608
00:43:38,740 --> 00:43:40,640
I have no family name.

609
00:43:42,159 --> 00:43:43,959
Call me A'Li.

